name: XPRO @ IFA 2022
description:
Never forget your visit at XPRO Berlin 2022! 
XPRO Berlin offers an complementary immersive Collectible rendered as a beautiful 3D video. 
Scan the QR code or go to xpro-zaubar.world to enter your ETH wallet address to receive your custom Collectible NFT as a memento of your time with us. 
Only for visitors to the XPRO Berlin booth at IFA. 
EXCLUSIVE NFT 
Powered by ZAUBAR, a Berlin-based start-up that makes time travel possible.
